== English ==
=== Etymology ===
[[address]] + [[-ability]]

=== Noun ===
'''addressability'''
# (''[[computer graphics]]'') the capability of a [[display surface]] or [[storage device]] to accommodate a specified number of uniquely identifiable points<ref name="1037c">[http://www.its.bldrdoc.gov/fs-1037/fs-1037c.htm Federal Standard 1037C]</ref>.
# (''[[micrographics]]'') the capability of a specified [[field frame]] to contain a specific number of uniquely identifiable points<ref name="1037c" />.

